text: Juan José Wedel was an archer from Costa Rica. He was born on 28 June 1944 and died on 20 November 2013. José Wedel competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics and at the 1980 Summer Olympics.Juan José WedelJuan WEDEL == References == Category:1944 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Costa Rican archers Category:Olympians for Costa Rica Category:Sportspeople from San José, Costa Rica
